  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct evaluated under the Minimal profile. The intended use scope — static structural performance prediction for a Class II non-cannulated pedicle screw system in compression-bending per ASTM F1717 — is described in the bound Requirement and Claim nodes. The FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; one factor (Test conditions) below required level due to single test condition.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/req/f1717-compression-bending-noncannulated",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/claim/fea-f1717-static-performance",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/model/pedicle-screw-fea-ensemble",
